Perfect for all book lovers and introverts who relate to the feeling of leaving your book behind to join the world. The design is both humorous and relatable, making it an ideal gift for anyone who enjoys literature and reading. Whether you prefer fiction or non-fiction, this design celebrates the joy of getting lost in a good book. Bring a touch of literary charm to your wardrobe with this unique and fun embroidered design. Introducing our trendy Garment Dyed Tee. Unisex fit with a vintage feel that improves with wear. Made from high-quality materials and featuring a unique print. Upgrade your wardrobe with this timeless piece.
fields.bullet_1:
100% Ring Spun Cotton with 100% Cotton Threads
 Soft washed, garment dyed fabric that brings extra coziness to your wardrobe.
fields.bullet_2: To wash this shirt, it is recommended to turn the shirt inside out and wash with cold water. It is also recommended to air dry this shirt, but the shirt can be placed in the dryer if necessary on tumble dry, low heat. Do not bleach, do not dry clean, and do not iron directly on the design!
fields.bullet_3: Great to pair with any casual outfit.
fields.bullet_4: Size up for an oversized look.  See the size chart for more details.
fields.import_description: made in the USA and imported
